# Default Setup Skill

When the user asks to bootstrap, initialize, or set up this lab (including `/lab-init`), prefer the `lab-init` project skill first.
For non-Cursor setup, use the `lab-os` CLI: `npx lab-os@latest init --target <path>`.

Trigger phrases include:
- `/lab-init`
- `bootstrap this lab`
- `initialize this project`
- `set up this repo`
- `first-time setup`

If the user explicitly requests a different workflow, follow the user override.
